						               													<description>It's the matching game you love, now featuring Color Character Cards that add new levels of strategy and power! Claim one of the four color power cards to fortify yourself with abilities that strengthen your position! Comes with a full set of UNO cards, which includes 16 Wild Color Character Cards! These cards allow you to take hold of the powers &amp;ndash; but make sure to use them when you can because anyone who plays a Wild Color Character can take that corresponding Color Power Card from another player! Game comes with 4 card holders to display your powers while you have them. You'll score points for each round in which you're the first to get rid of all the cards in your hand, and the first player or team to 500 wins. When you're down to one card, don't forget to yell &amp;quot;UNO!&amp;quot; Game contains 112 cards (including character cards and wild cards), card holders, and instructions. For 2 to 10 players, ages 7 and older. Easy to pick up, impossible to put down.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's the classic matching card game, now with special characters that bring special powers!&amp;#10;Players take turns matching one of their cards with the color or number card shown on the top of the deck.&amp;#10;Special Color Power Cards offer special powers, but opponents with wild character cards might steal the power cards from you!&amp;#10;Score points by being the first to get rid of all the cards in your hand.&amp;#10;First player or team to 500 wins.&amp;#10;UNO is easy to pick up, impossible to put down!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
